name: PMMR Performance Indicators FY2013-15 (Historical Data)
creator: NYC OpenData
description: This data contains all indicator data from the PY13-FY15 Preliminary Mayor's Management Reports (meaning all data from performance indicators related to each agency's work, not including budgeting and agency resource data). The full text of the FY13-15 PMMRs, archived reports, and additional information is available at https://www1.nyc.gov/site/operations/performance/mmr.page.

name: 2011 Yellow Taxi Trip Data
creator: NYC OpenData
description: These records are generated from the trip record submissions made by yellow taxi Technology Service Providers (TSPs). Each row represents a single trip in a yellow taxi. The trip records include fields capturing pick-up and drop-off dates/times, pick-up and drop-off taxi zone locations, trip distances, itemized fares, rate types, payment types, and driver-reported passenger counts.
